Set mysql default coding method to UTF-8:
    (1). modify the mysql configuration file in /etc/mysql/conf.d/mysql.cnf
    Adding the following line:
        [mysql]
        default-character-set=utf8

        [client]
        default-character-set=utf8 

        [mysqld]
        character-set-server = utf8
    (2). restart mysql service usinng the init script
        $ sudo /etc/init.d/mysql restart/start/stop

